translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  28,51,"Soni chisimu pamasile pa twalunguchisye ŵanganyao maloŵe (gachamuko jajili Qur’an), kuti mwine takumbuchile (nambo kwapi)"
  28,52,"Aŵala ŵanakwapaga chitabu kala jalakwe (Qur’an) nkanijiyiche, ŵanganyao jalakwe akujikulupilila (mpela ‘Abdullâh bin Salâm ni Salmân Al-Fârisî)"
  28,53,"Soni pati jichisoomedwaga kukwao akasatiji: “Uwwe tujikulupilile jalakwe, yalakweyi niyakuona yakuumila kwa M’mbuje gwetu, chisimu uwwe namuno nkanijiŵe jalakweji, twaliji Asilamu (ŵakuya Musa ni Isa).”"
  28,54,"Ŵanganyao tachipedwa malipilo gao kaŵilikose ligongo lya kupilila kwao, ni akutyosyaga ni yambone yakusakala, nambo soni mu ichindu yatwapele akasatolaga"
  28,55,"Soni pati apikene yangali mate akasaiŵambalaga ni akasatiji: “Uwwe tukwete masengo getu, nombe jenumanja nkwete masengo genu. Ntendele uŵe kukwenu. Uwwe ŵangasachilila (kwakuya) ajinga.”"
  28,56,"Chisimu mmwe nganim’ba mun’jongwele jwamunnonyele, nambo Allah akun’jongolaga jwakunsaka, soni Jwalakwe ni jwaakwamanya chenene akongoka"
  28,57,"Sano ŵanganyao ni ŵatite: “Naga tukuye chongoko chan’di nacho chituswambidwe m’chilambo mwetu.” Ana nganitwatamilikachisya ŵanganyao malo gakuchimbichika gantunjelele (Maaka), kwaikwika mwalulele isogosi yamitundumitundu kuŵa lisiki lyakuuma Kukwetu? Nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ngakumanyilila"
  28,58,"Soni jilingwajilingwa mwa misi jatwajijonasile, janakutwanjilaga ndamo jao (jambone)! Sanotu amo nimmalo mwao mwanganimutamidweje panyuma pao ikaŵeje panandipe, soni Uwwe niŵatwaliji Ŵawinjila"
  28,59,"Ni nganaŵa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ŵanti nikonanga misi mpaka akatumisye mu nsinda wakwe wekulungwa ntenga jwakwasoomela ŵanganyao ma Ȃya Getu (nkugakanamo nikwajonangaga), soni nganituŵa ŵakujijonanga misi ikaŵeje achimisyeneo ali ŵalupuso"